headline: Is Nasdaq (NDAQ) Priced Fairly After Recent Share Price Pullback?
summary: If you are wondering whether Nasdaq's current share price reflects its true worth, you are not alone, especially with a lot of attention on exchanges and market infrastructure right now. Nasdaq last closed at US$82.49, with returns of 4.0% over 1 year, 46.9% over 3 years and 84.0% over 5 years, although the stock has seen a 6.0% decline over 7 days, 16.0% over 30 days and 14.7% year to date.
